Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:01.64,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:06.64,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,There were another 23 victims yesterday, again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:12.74,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the possibility of Kira being a student is put forward, the timing of the murders change to indicate that this isn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:15.70,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means that Kira must have access to police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:22.87,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Now that L knows I'm somehow getting police information, without doubt, he'll use the police as a link to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.81,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,There's a human that's been following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.96,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.13,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get rid of him as soon as possible, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:39.80,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami's eyes have the ability to see a person's name and life span, just by looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:40.72,Note,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:40.91,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Also, {\alpha&HFF&}Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:51.30,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes is... {\alpha&HFF&}half of your remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes is... half of your remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:01:00.03,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want to do, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.04,SIGN,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(362,361)}The Chase
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.29,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen Ryuk around lately, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:09.76,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Was he serious about having dropped his Death Note on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:12.68,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been picked up by a human before he got to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:19.41,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,No way! If he did something like that, he'd be forced to watch over them until either the human dies, or the notebook is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:23.49,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. There's no way Ryuk could be bothered to do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:27.65,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I heard he's got two Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.59,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! Why the hell has he got two?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:32.90,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:37.49,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, {\alpha&HFF&}I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... {\alpha&HFF&}right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:45.02,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so what do ya wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.33,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Have we got a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:50.69,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.. {\alpha&HFF&}that deal is... out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.. that deal is... {\alpha&HFF&}out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.. that deal is... out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:54.46,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.02,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to create a new ideal world, free of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.44,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,And I intend to reign as God of that new world for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.03,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If the deal had involved increasing my life span, I might have considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.86,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,But anything that decreases it isn't even worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:24.39,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have thought that you'd already know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:29.28,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, I just wanted to tell you that the deal exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:33.54,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Thought I'd better tell you this sort of thing early on, so I don't have to put up with your complaints later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.88,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you'd better tell me this sort of thing "early on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.18,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it already slightly late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:42.36,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me this either as soon as we met, {\alpha&HFF&}or written it as part of the explanations in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me this either as soon as we met, or written it as part of the explanations in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.03,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.85,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't fear me in the slightest, even though I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:56.90,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't try to suck up to me, and he keeps on relentlessly asking such probing questions of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:02.76,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:08.25,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else you should have told me beforehand, Ryuk the Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.62,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.08,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:14.60,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.75,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,A shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.90,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If it was wings instead of eyes, {\alpha&HFF&}I might have seriously considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was wings instead of eyes, I might have seriously considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It seems quite fitting for a god to have wings and fly freely across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's been man's dream since antiquity to be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.74,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,If you grew wings and flew around you'd stand out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:35.63,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,The police would probably be able to catch you purely on that basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.11,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I was joking, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:42.81,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,With all the trading of eyes, wings or whatever, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd probably end up becoming a real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the trading of eyes, wings or whatever, I'd probably end up becoming a real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.49,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I guess that could be quite an interesting concept too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.54,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.58,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Even without doing anything like that, {\alpha&HFF&}you're already a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without doing anything like that, you're already {\alpha&HFF&}a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without doing anything like that, you're already a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.84,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the World of Shinigami is rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They live a vague and pointless existence, only taking human lives because they, themselves, are afraid to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.81,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,They no longer understand why they even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.25,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably no meaning in their existence at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.20,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to them, Light, {\alpha&HFF&}you're more of a Shinigami than they'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to them, Light, you're more of a Shinigami than they'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:30.29,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Well, by the sound of things, I'm doing a lot more work than them, {\alpha&HFF&}but I wouldn't want to be compared to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, by the sound of things, I'm doing a lot more work than them, but I wouldn't want to be compared to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:37.32,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,As a human, I'm using the Death Note to help humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:44.75,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't like the World of Shinigami is of little importance to the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.35,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.86,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth. {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuk, even if Shinigami like you come down just once every hundred — no, thousand — years, the human world will change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth. Ryuk, even if Shinigami like you come down just once every hundred — no, thousand — years, the human world will change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.63,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The existence of the World of Shinigami is extremely significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.19,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:06.09,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If the World of Shinigami is really as rotten as you say it is, Ryuk, {\alpha&HFF&}why don't you try changing things when you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the World of Shinigami is really as rotten as you say it is, Ryuk, why don't you try changing things when you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.50,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Light, {\alpha&HFF&}you're turning out to be quite the positive thinker..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you're turning out to be quite the positive thinker..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.97,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:26.84,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be a positive thinker to think of using the Death Note to personally right the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.26,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.50,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.10,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? What do you "get"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.90,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out how to obtain the name of my stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.65,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.97,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be using the rules of the Death Note to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:53.91,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes and 40 seconds are granted to write any further details".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.23,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,First, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll need to test just how free I am to specify the details of the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll need to test just how free I am to specify the details of the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.34,MINOR SIGN,MINOR SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(356,394)\fad(700,0)}The next day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.26,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.54,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Another six prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.84,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Due to heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.96,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:17.52,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.44,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Three of them exhibited a pattern of behavior before death that we've never seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.39,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.32,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it wasn't just a normal heart attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.11,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,No. The cause of death was definitely a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.64,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,But directly before it happened, {\alpha&HFF&}one of them cut his own finger and drew a strange picture on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But directly before it happened, one of them cut his own finger and drew a strange picture on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.33,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Another left an unexplainable note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:42.84,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,The third managed to escape and seems to have made the effort to run all the way to the staff toilets before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.45,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:54.97,Default,Watari,0000,0000,0000,,A few heart attack victims that acted slightly different from the usual have just been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.02,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Different from the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.66,Default,Watari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you the images of the text and picture they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.02,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:06.67,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,This reads as though he's afraid of Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:12.50,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It could conceivably be merely the actions of a criminal, {\alpha&HFF&}but if Kira can control the time of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could conceivably be merely the actions of a criminal, but if Kira can control the time of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:18.97,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What if Kira can also control the movements leading up to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.16,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.28,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, {\alpha&HFF&}regarding the most recent victims, I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, regarding the most recent victims, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, regarding the most recent victims, I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:35.99,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that Kira may be using these criminals to conduct some kind of test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.91,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,And if that is the case, {\alpha&HFF&}we shouldn't give them any easy answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that is the case, we shouldn't give them any easy answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:42.54,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.65,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.80,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Performing tests on criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.56,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.97,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as though they enjoy playing games with people's lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.61,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:08:00.48,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira's really experimenting on criminals... {\alpha&HFF&}what's their objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira's really experimenting on criminals... what's their objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:10.51,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:16.35,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The results of yesterday's six tests have already been entered into dad's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:20.64,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note is even more useful than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.64,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What d'ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.69,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Having escaped, one of them ran to a toilet that I'd specified in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:31.44,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Another drew the exact picture that I'd drawn in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:35.86,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,And another wrote the same sentences that I wrote in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:40.45,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Those three did exactly what I intended them to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.29,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,For the remaining three, I purposely wrote circumstances that would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:51.10,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,First, I wrote that the victim would die in an hour's time in front of the Eiffel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:56.68,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's physically impossible for a prisoner in Japan to reach France in just an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.18,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, this doesn't actually happen, and the victim simply dies of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:05.98,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I wrote "Draws an exact picture of L's face on the wall" in the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's impossible to draw somebody you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.57,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:19.12,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly, I specified that the final victim should write, "I know that L is suspicious of the police force".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:23.44,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that this one might work, but it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:31.50,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If someone doesn't know a piece of information, they can't think of it, and so it'd be unnatural for that person to write it down, meaning they won't be able to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:36.06,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Death Note cannot accomplish the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:43.60,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,But, if it's within the realistic limits of what they can do, I can control them as much as I like before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:48.85,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,I've got that much, but what are ya trying to achieve, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.61,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,L and the police will never be able to guess my true objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:59.70,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The famous detective will be too busy investigating the mystery of those pictures and messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:03.70,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Those completely meaningless "dying messages".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:11.92,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is really using criminals as test subjects, it must be because they're about to begin something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.13,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If they make a move now, {\alpha&HFF&}there's the possibility that their suspicious actions will be picked up by the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they make a move now, there's the possibility that their suspicious actions will be picked up by the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.12,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}If there's another reason they're doing this, other than to run tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... If there's another reason they're doing this, other than to run tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.86,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a message in the drawings and text.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:28.94,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:32.44,Note,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,The upper line reads "L, did you know?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's finally time for the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.28,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Real deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.28,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this drug addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:43.83,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, he attempted to rob a bank, but failed to take any money, and escaped by shooting employees and members of the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.08,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's slightly last minute, but I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.25,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try asking a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.60,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"Try asking a few people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.78,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. {\alpha&HFF&}Despite my appearance, I'm actually quite popular with the ladies, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Despite my appearance, I'm actually quite popular with the ladies, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,..Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Light?! Good morning.
Comment: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:34.25,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,He's still following me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:40.13,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't, what I'm about to do would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.76,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,A date, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:49.43,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,However you look at it, it's just a normal date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.52,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Even the guy that's following me can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.27,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't just a "normal" date, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:01.07,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned something about knowing how to figure out your stalker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.99,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.78,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Ryuk? {\alpha&HFF&}Didn't you see what I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Ryuk? Didn't you see what I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:12.62,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,No. Otherwise it'd be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.75,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, just be patient and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.61,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Have you been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I haven't been to Space Land since Junior High!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And we get to spend the entire day together, just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.65,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,If he goes out on a weekday, he either goes to school or cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.14,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,On the odd day off, he goes on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.86,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Seems pretty normal. An earnest final year exam student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.19,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Police Chief Yagami's son, Light - {\alpha&HFF&}no need for suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police Chief Yagami's son, Light - no need for suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:54.86,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just check his movements today, and then that'll be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:04.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But Light, didn't you say that we weren't going to go out until the exams are over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.09,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay, since I placed first in the national mock exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Eww, no need to be so smug.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.78,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:45.80,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.39,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Seven passengers, excluding him... {\alpha&HFF&}in that case, everything should proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven passengers, excluding him... in that case, everything should proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.98,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking over this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.40,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,A bus hi-jack?! At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:07.74,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down! I'll kill anyone who dares to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:13.32,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, driver! D'ya know the phone number of the Space Land offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.75,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Call 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:14.75,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.71,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,This is driver Sasaki, of bus number 124.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.91,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Tell 'em what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.07,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I've been hi-hacked by a man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been hi-hacked by a man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.22,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Give it 'ere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.88,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what's going on? Now, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:37.73,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,I want a woman in a car to bring yesterday's takings to the bus stop two stops away from Space Land before this bus gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:44.50,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,If you call the police, or try anything funny, I'll kill every single person on this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:55.70,LongNote,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20.338983}Yuri-chan, don't worry; it's okay. \NI'll find an opportunity to disarm him. \NMy father's a police officer and I've \Nlearnt how to counter-attack such a scenario. \NHe looks small and relatively weak. \NI'm stronger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:57.68,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-chan, don't worry; it's okay. I'll find an opportunity to disarm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.71,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, it's too dangerous. Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.88,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to that, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.63,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, you don't need to communicate in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.05,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,The noise of the bus is enough to cover up hushed conversations from the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:15.85,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any proof that you're not an accomplice to this crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:17.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.81,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fairly common practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:27.02,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit fools us into thinking he's alone, but secretly plants an accomplice at the back, just in case anything goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.86,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, no way, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:32.83,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.54,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.64,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,If he was, then he'd be able to kill the culprit with a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.96,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my proof. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.86,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:51.88,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So that's who L's been using to investigate the Japanese police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,His name is {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.53,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll trust you, {\alpha&HFF&}and for the time being I won't question what an FBI agent is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll trust you, and for the time being I won't question what an FBI agent is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.35,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.77,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.30,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So if it comes to that, I'll be relying on you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.03,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:14.95,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up! Do ya wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:16.91,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,That man! {\alpha&HFF&}He was on the Japanese news two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man! He was on the Japanese news two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:24.92,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,He robbed a bank, killed three people, and then fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.04,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,He's extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.45,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. {\alpha&HFF&}He'll never shoot us with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. He'll never shoot us with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.89,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, you! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.64,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,What's on that bit of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.30,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--! {\alpha&HFF&}You passing notes around to try plotting against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--! You passing notes around to try plotting against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.10,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! {\alpha&HFF&}If he finds that note from before... he'll realize that we're waiting for an opportunity to overpower him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! If he finds that note from before... he'll realize that we're waiting for an opportunity to overpower him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.99,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Just arrangements for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.89,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,What a load of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:58.62,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.33,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.25,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,You! The guy right at the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.47,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.05,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Since when have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:20.03,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.27,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.68,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! {\alpha&HFF&}I-I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! I-{\alpha&HFF&}I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! I-I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.15,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.. he's hallucinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.29,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.53,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:41.37,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,That note with the arrangements for the date was written on paper from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:46.67,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,And he made this guy touch it, so this guy's the only one who's able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.46,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.00,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.15,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:57.26,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm a Shinigami, so things like that won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.44,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who touch the Death Note are able to see me."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.91,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"I will always have to follow Light around."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.90,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinigami won't die just by being shot."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.66,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,These are all things I've told Light in the past, {\alpha&HFF&}and this is just the kind of practical application I'd expect from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all things I've told Light in the past, and this is just the kind of practical application I'd expect from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:32.84,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,And he's managed to use this hi-jacking to get the name of the guy that's been following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.47,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:06.67,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly 11:45.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.33,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.50,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Oosoreda Kiichirou... death by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:22.64,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Boards the 11:31-bus to Space Land from the bus station at the east entrance to the park, with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:30.06,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Appears to have some out-of-this-world type of hallucination and empties his gun towards it. Disembarks from the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:36.28,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately afterwards; same day; 11:45 - dies in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:44.14,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.90,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn next... {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn next... Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(565,302)}To be continued
